      "span_text": "However, the affine mirabolic bimodule R aff over the affine Hecke algebra H aff is not free (see Remark 1) . Recall that H aff can be realized in the equivariant K-homology of the Steinberg variety. It would be very interesting to find a similar realization of R aff . Finally let us mention that the results of this note are very closely related to the results of [CITATION_1] , though our motivations are rather different."
