      "span_text": "Since the Schubert varieties in the mirabolic affine Grassmannian are equisingular to the orbit closures in the enhanced nilpotent cone (see 3.7, 3.8) , the appearance of Shoji's polynomials in the spherical mirabolic bimodule and in the mirabolic Hall bimodule is an immediate corollary of [CITATION_3] ."
